    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_10_20661-20687",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "20661-20687",
      "markText": "但随着年龄的增长，请尽量避免使用它。这非常消耗能量。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=20661&rangeEnd=20687",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=20661&rangeEnd=20687"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_9_16224-16288",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "16224-16288",
      "markText": "我们必须感谢生活在不同的时代，即使在今天，一想到这些来之不易的自由所受到的威胁，我们就会不寒而栗。也许谨言慎行依然是默认的秩序。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=16224&rangeEnd=16288",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=16224&rangeEnd=16288"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_9_11954-12083",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "11954-12083",
      "markText": "知识和经济背景下诞生的11。克服有害的情感，比如非理性的激情的唯一希望是用另一种由理性触发的更强的积极情感去压倒它。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11954&rangeEnd=12083",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11954&rangeEnd=12083"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_10_15172-15268",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "15172-15268",
      "markText": "为什么一些人会成为领导，而另一些人则成为下属？为什么一些人值得尊重，而另一些人则畏缩不前？这与知识或技能关系不大，而与某个人的某些身体特征和行为方式，以及如何激起他人的某些情绪反应有很大关系。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=15172&rangeEnd=15268",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=15172&rangeEnd=15268"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_10_2999-3029",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2999-3029",
      "markText": "我们先有情绪，再有感受，因为进化首先产生情绪，然后才有感受。",
      "totalCount": 88,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2999&rangeEnd=3029",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2999&rangeEnd=3029"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_10_7137-7169",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "7137-7169",
      "markText": "用斯宾诺莎自己的话说：“每个事物莫不尽其所能，以努力保持其存在”",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7137&rangeEnd=7169",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7137&rangeEnd=7169"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_9_3002-3048",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3002-3048",
      "markText": "情绪与感受是一对双胞胎，情绪是头生子，感受是次生子，并且，感受永远尾随于情绪之后，如影随形。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3002&rangeEnd=3048",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3002&rangeEnd=3048"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_9_13986-14080",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "13986-14080",
      "markText": "斯宾诺莎告诉我们，每个人都有权思考自己感兴趣的话题，说出自己思考的内容，然而这并非一件短期内就能做到的事，至少目前不行。当心，小心你所说的（以及你所写的），否则，连你的遗骨都将不再属于你。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13986&rangeEnd=14080",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13986&rangeEnd=14080"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_11_1150-1227",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1150-1227",
      "markText": "请你想象自己躺在沙滩上，傍晚的阳光轻轻地温暖着你的皮肤，大海的波浪拍打着你的脚背，松针在你身后沙沙作响，夏日的微风拂过，气温是温和的25摄氏度，万里无云。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1150&rangeEnd=1227",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1150&rangeEnd=1227"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_9_3767-3851",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3767-3851",
      "markText": "生活如同一场高空钢索表演，大部分感受都体现出为保持平衡所做出的努力，以及进行细微调节、纠错的想法，倘若没有感受，即使是一个微小的失误也会铸成大错，整个表演都将宣告失败。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300051264&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3767&rangeEnd=3851",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23b32c20813ab7a86g014c6c?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3767&rangeEnd=3851"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300051264_6_3452-3526",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3452-3526",
      "markText": "归根结底，还是个体要处理它与“整全”之间的关系问题。这套关系是连续的谱系，从低级的细胞膜行为——称为“情绪”，演化为高级的信仰行为——称为“精神”。",
